    "name": "Ai Yamamoto",
    "profile": "Ai Yamamoto  \r\n\r\nAi yamamoto has been composing since 2001. Her music style varies from soft melodic and shimmering abstract melodies to dark explosive tones. Her main area of interest is the dramatic structure and flow of music as well as gentle melodies with abstract texture which bring atmospheric sound scape in her compositions. \r\nShe worked with Lawrence English, Raceless AKA Curse of Dialect, Ben Frost, Sofi Basseghi (video artists), Steve Law, Bita Fayyazi (performance, video artist), an tuong nguyen(video artist), and more!\r\n",
